{"tid":1325261,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"候選港姐梁敏巧原來參加過2014年學聯罷課，女神呀","createTime":"2019-07-16T22:58:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T00:25:04.000Z","uid":270466,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9135cea2e5d152195fc453c625b8a3906b692067","tid":1325261,"uid":270466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T22:58:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190714/59824159\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190714%2F59824159&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufST%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=f0f93a1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190714%2F59824159&h=d9c9facb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190714/59824159</a><br />\n候選港姐梁敏巧喺IG寫感受︰「近來社會運動遍地開花，充斥極端情緒，的確令人擔憂，因今次事件而失去的人命，亦令人好痛心。原來好多香港人仍然咁愛香港，咁關心社會，唔止年輕人，仲包括各階層的人。」同時，她又提出自己觀點：「每個人都有不同意見立場，我們不是機械人，無可能要求所有人思想一致。每個人都有自己的選擇，我相信每個人有獨立思考能力，明白行動所帶來嘅後果，最重要香港人本質是熱愛這片土地。」她又寄望：「願港人仍可擁抱自由民主、人權法治、公平公義、多元包容、尊重個人和恪守專業。」<br />\n<br />\n女神好犀利，原來佢2014年參加過學聯發起嘅罷課，當年台灣公視都有報道過<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/62p2ysY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F62p2ysY.png&h=c1452126&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n睇片就1:42開始睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.pts.org.tw/article/279807?NEENO=279807\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.pts.org.tw%2Farticle%2F279807%3FNEENO%3D279807&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufST%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=523a6d7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.pts.org.tw/article/279807?NEENO=279807</a><br />\n<br />\n佢話佢參選係想好似麥明詩咁有影響力，希望佢選到啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a